Mithril js

Installation:

$sudo apt-get install npm
$sudo apt-get install nodejs-legacy
$npm i -g http-server
$git clone https://github.com/llambda/mithril-modal.git
$cd mithril-modal
$npm i
$npm run watch
$hs
$open http://localhost:3000/demo.html



